==English==
=== Etymology ===
From [[gyro-]] and [[-scope]]

=== Noun ===
#an apparatus composed of a wheel which spins inside of a frame (gimbal) and causes the balancing of the frame in any direction or position. Often used in helping to keep aircraft and ships steady.

